        {
            "title": "私會中國商人遭曝光 秘魯臨時總統面臨罷免危機",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"私會中國商人遭曝光 秘魯臨時總統面臨罷免危機\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jvj6AWNOAuOcSu4Z9FoHdg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/14b377a0-f722-11f0-b775-a8b0c6c08c7d\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">私會中國商人遭曝光 秘魯臨時總統面臨罷免危機</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
