            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"[川普達沃斯講話精選]和習近平關係好；美股會翻番；格陵蘭框架達成\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8WbeqLqbhZNuVghg19XcOQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/fc9579c0-f6ea-11f0-bfb8-59c518c4c76b\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">[川普達沃斯講話精選]和習近平關係好；美股會翻番；格陵蘭框架達成</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
